              <!-- Panel 1: The Process -->
              <div id="faqpanel1" class="faq-panel">
                <details class="faq-item" open>
                  <summary>How does the process work from start to finish? <span class="faq-icon"></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">Simple and transparent. We start with a free 30-minute strategy call to understand your business and goals. Once the contract is signed we start immediately — no waiting, no delays. The build runs as a focused 3-week sprint with full visibility at every stage.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>What do you need from me to get started? <span class="faq-icon"></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">Just the basics — your business goals, target audience, and any branding you already have such as a logo, colors, or photos. We will contact you for any additional information we need along the way. No branding yet? We can handle that too as part of our <a href="/services/branding-creative-design" class="inline-service-link">branding service</a>.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>Will I be involved during the build? <span class="faq-icon"></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">Yes, and your involvement makes the difference. We share progress at every stage of the design — header, footer, sections — as each part is completed. To keep the project moving on schedule, we ask that you review each finished stage promptly and provide your feedback before we move to the next one. This keeps us inside the 3-week timeline and avoids delays on both sides.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>What if I already have a website? <span class="faq-icon"></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">We will audit it first. If it has a solid foundation we can redesign and optimize it. If it is holding your business back we will recommend a full rebuild and tell you exactly why.</p>
                </details>
              </div>

              <!-- Panel 2: Design & Performance -->
              <div id="faqpanel2" class="faq-panel">
                <details class="faq-item" open>
                  <summary>Will my website be custom or template-based? <span class="faq-icon"></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">We prefer building fully custom websites tailored to your brand and goals — that is how we deliver the best results. In some cases, if a template strictly fits your requirements and budget, we can work with one. We will always recommend the approach that serves your business best and be transparent about which direction we are taking.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>How fast will my website load? <span class="faq-icon"></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">For custom-built static sites and landing pages we guarantee under 2 seconds. For WooCommerce e-commerce builds we target 2.5 to 3 seconds or less. Speed depends on the project requirements — page length, features, and content — but we guarantee we will always do our best to deliver the fastest possible result for your specific build.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>Will my website work on mobile? <span class="faq-icon"></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">Every layout starts at mobile. We design for the phone in your customer's hand first, then scale up to tablet and desktop. Mobile-first is not optional — it is how we build everything.</p>
                </details>
                <details class="faq-item">
                  <summary>Will it be SEO-friendly? <span class="faq-icon"></span></summary>
                  <p class="faq-answer">Every website we build includes solid SEO foundations — proper structure, meta tags, fast load times, and local schema markup. This alone brings faster traffic, leads, and conversions compared to a poorly built site. For deeper results, we also offer a dedicated <a href="/services/seo-website-optimization" class="inline-service-link">SEO service</a> that goes far beyond what is built into the website itself. We will let you know what makes sense for your goals.</p>
